		{ ref: `Proverbs 31:25`, slug: `proverbs`, ch: 31, text: `She is clothed with strength and dignity, and she can laugh without fear of the days to come.`, note: `Your real strength isn't in doing it all — it's the quiet dignity of a daughter who can face tomorrow unafraid.` },
		{ ref: `Zephaniah 3:17`, slug: `zephaniah`, ch: 3, text: `Your Father is in your midst, a mighty one who will save; He will rejoice over you with gladness and quiet you with His love; He will sing over you.`, note: `Picture it: your Father actually delights in you — He quiets your weary heart and sings over you like a song.` },
		{ ref: `1 Peter 3:3-4`, slug: `1-peter`, ch: 3, text: `Let your beauty not be only outward, but the unfading beauty of a gentle and quiet spirit — which is precious in your Father's sight.`, note: `The world grades your appearance; your Father treasures the heart inside you that never fades.` },
		{ ref: `Isaiah 43:1`, slug: `isaiah`, ch: 43, text: `Fear not, for I have redeemed you; I have called you by name — you are Mine, says your Father.`, note: `You're not a role or a to-do list to Him. He knows your name, and He calls you His own.` },
		{ ref: `Psalm 46:5`, slug: `psalms`, ch: 46, text: `God is within her; she will not be shaken. God will help her at the break of day.`, note: `When everything is leaning on you, your Father is within you — you will not be shaken, and morning mercy is coming.` },
